bgDescription: A fried rice that every family in Jinzhou knows how to make. It’s made in a way that each rice has a golden layer of fired egg yolk on the outside for the good luck. Therefore, it also becomes a good-luck dish for festive dinners down the mines that carries the workers’ wish that their toil and frugality may bring peace and fortune for them and their families.
description: Reduce Wall Dash and swimming stamina consumption for all Resonators in the team by 20% for 30 minutes. This effect only applies on your own characters in Co-op Mode.
